UMVIKELI Womphakathi u-Adv Busisiwe Mkhwebane usethole ukuthi umengameli wakuleli uMnuz Cyril Ramaphosa wakhohlisa iphalamende ngodaba lomnikelo kaR500 000 owanikelwa yiBosasa ixhasa imikhakhaso yakhe yokuba ngumengameli we-ANC. Ngesikhathi ethula umbiko wakhe ngoLwesihlanu uMkhwebane uveze ukuthi uRamaphosa wakhohlisa iphalamende ngoNovemba nyakenye ngesikhathi ephekwa ngemibuzo ngokuthola imali kwiBosasa esolwa ngenkohlakalo nokugwazela izikhulu zikahulumeni. “Singakuqinisekisa obekusolwa ngokuthi umengameli Ramaphosa wakhohlisa iphalamende ngemabomu ngo-Novemba 6, 2018. Umengameli wakhohlisa iphalamende ngemabomu ngoba wayengazinikeza isikhathi sokuthi aphenye kabanzi athole impendulo eqondile ngombuzo ayebuzwa wona,” kusho uMkhwebane. UMkhwebane uthe umengameli uphule umthethosisekelo ngalesi senzo. UMvikeli Womphakathi wethule lo mbiko kulandela isikhalo samaqembu aphikisayo sokuthi uRamaphosa wayehubhuza amanga ngamabomu ngesikhathi ethi indodana yakhe, u-Andile, eyathola inkontileka kaR500 000 neBosasa. URamaphosa wabuye wabhalela iphalamende ehoxisa impendulo yakhe wathi empeleni le mali yanikelwa yiBosasa ezinhlelweni zakhe zokukhankasela ukuba umengameli we-ANC. 